<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Reduce Food Waste</title>
    <script src="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/lucide/0.263.1/lucide.min.js"></script>
    <style>
        * { margin: 0; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box; }
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            background-color: #f5f5f5;
        }
        .navbar {
            background: #fff;
            padding: 1rem 2rem;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: center;
            box-shadow: 0 2px 5px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
            position: fixed;
            width: 100%;
            top: 0;
            z-index: 1000;
        }
        .logo {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 0.5rem;
            color: #4CAF50;
            text-decoration: none;
            font-weight: bold;
            font-size: 1.5rem;
        }
        .nav-links {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 2rem;
        }
        .nav-links a {
            text-decoration: none;
            color: #333;
        }
        .sign-up {
            background: #ff4444;
            color: white;
            padding: 0.5rem 1rem;
            border-radius: 5px;
        }
        .hero {
            margin-top: 60px;
            background: linear-gradient(rgba(0,0,0,0.6), rgba(0,0,0,0.6)), url('images/home.jpeg');
            background-size: cover;
            background-position: center;
            height: 70vh;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            text-align: center;
            color: white;
            padding: 2rem;
            position: relative;
            overflow: hidden;
        }
        .hero h1 {
            font-size: 3.5rem;
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
            text-shadow: 2px 2px 4px rgba(0,0,0,0.5);
        }
        .hero h2 {
            font-size: 2.5rem;
            color: #4CAF50;
            text-shadow: 2px 2px 4px rgba(0,0,0,0.5);
        }
        .features {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(280px, 1fr));
            gap: 2rem;
            padding: 4rem 2rem;
            max-width: 1200px;
            margin: 0 auto;
        }
        .feature-card {
            background: white;
            border-radius: 15px;
            overflow: hidden;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
            transition: transform 0.3s;
        }
        .feature-card:hover {
            transform: translateY(-5px);
        }
        .feature-image {
            width: 100%;
            height: 200px;
            overflow: hidden;
            position: relative;
        }
        .feature-image img {
            width: 100%;
            height: 100%;
            object-fit: cover;
            transition: transform 0.3s;
        }
        .feature-card:hover .feature-image img {
            transform: scale(1.1);
        }
        .feature-content {
            padding: 1.5rem;
        }
        .feature-content h3 {
            color: #333;
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
            font-size: 1.5rem;
        }
        .feature-content p {
            color: #666;
            margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
        }
        .button {
            display: inline-block;
            padding: 0.8rem 1.5rem;
            background: #4CAF50;
            color: white;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 5px;
            transition: all 0.3s;
        }
        .button:hover {
            background: #45a049;
            transform: translateY(-2px);
        }
        footer {
            background: #4CAF50;
            color: white;
            text-align: center;
            padding: 3rem 2rem;
        }
        .social-links {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            gap: 2rem;
            margin-top: 2rem;
        }
        .social-links a {
            color: white;
            background: rgba(255,255,255,0.1);
            width: 40px;
            height: 40px;
            border-radius: 50%;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            transition: all 0.3s;
        }
        .social-links a:hover {
            background: rgba(255,255,255,0.2);
            transform: translateY(-2px);
        }
        
        @media (max-width: 768px) {
            .hero h1 { font-size: 2.5rem; }
            .hero h2 { font-size: 1.8rem; }
            .features { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <nav class="navbar">
        <a href="#" class="logo">
            <i data-lucide="leaf" color="#4CAF50"></i>
            SavRY
        </a>
        <div class="nav-links">
            <a href="#">HOME</a>
            <a href="#">ABOUT</a>
            <a href="#">CONTACT</a>
            <% if (name) { %>
                <span>Welcome, <%= name %></span>
                <a href="/logout" class="sign-up">LOGOUT</a>
              <% } else { %>
                <a href="/signup" class="sign-up">SIGN UP</a>
                <a href="/donlogin" class="sign-up">LOGIN</a>
              <% } %>
        </div>
    </nav>

    <div class="hero">
        <h1>REDUCE FOOD WASTAGE THROUGH</h1>
        <h2>US FOR A BETTER TOMORROW</h2>
    </div>

    <div class="features">
        <div class="feature-card">
            <div class="feature-image">
                <img src="images/donate.png" alt="Food Donation">
            </div>
            <div class="feature-content">
                <i data-lucide="heart-handshake" size="48" color="#4CAF50"></i>
                <h3>Sell Excess Food to your community</h3>
                <p>Every day, tons of food go to waste while millions of people go hungry. Instead of throwing away excess food, donate it for slight profit and help others.</p>
                <a href="http://localhost:5173/" class="button">Donate Now</a>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="feature-card">
            <div class="feature-image">
                <img src="images/charity.png" alt="Charity Support">
            </div>
            <div class="feature-content">
                <i data-lucide="heart" size="48" color="#4CAF50"></i>
                <h3>Charity Food Donation</h3>
                <p>Donate to local shelters and help people through us.</p>
                <a href="/donation" class="button">Support Us</a>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="feature-card">
            <div class="feature-image">
                <img src="images/leftover.png" alt="Leftover Meals">
            </div>
            <div class="feature-content">
                <i data-lucide="utensils" size="48" color="#4CAF50"></i>
                <h3>Turn Leftovers into Meals</h3>
                <p>Transform extra food into creative and delicious meals while saving money and helping the environment.</p>
                <a href="/recipe" class="button">Get Recipes</a>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="feature-card">
            <div class="feature-image">
                <img src="images/recycle.png" alt="Recycling Tracker">
            </div>
            <div class="feature-content">
                <i data-lucide="recycle" size="48" color="#4CAF50"></i>
                <h3>Smart Recycling Tracker</h3>
                <p>Start making a difference with our Smart Recycling Tracker. Track your eco-friendly choices and earn rewards!</p>
                <a href="/recycle" class="button">Start Tracking</a>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="feature-card">
            <div class="feature-image">
                <img src="images/predict.png" alt="Food Waste Predictor">
            </div>
            <div class="feature-content">
                <i data-lucide="predict" size="48" color="#4CAF50"></i>
                <h3>Food waste Predictor</h3>
                <p>Predict the food waste that may be left after a event and plan accordingly!</p>
                <a href="http://127.0.0.1:5000" class="button">Start Tracking</a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    
    
</div>

    <footer>
        <h2>WASTE NOT WANT NOT!!</h2>
        <div class="social-links">
            <a href="#"><i data-lucide="facebook" size="24"></i></a>
            <a href="#"><i data-lucide="twitter" size="24"></i></a>
            <a href="#"><i data-lucide="instagram" size="24"></i></a>
            <a href="#"><i data-lucide="linkedin" size="24"></i></a>
        </div>
    </footer>

    <script>
        lucide.createIcons();
    </script>
</body>
</html>